notesStmt.note: This panel discussion takes place in a conference room at the university campus in Vienna. It is the final event of an international conference on gender studies. First, two speakers give a general overview of their impressions of the conference and address a number of issues and questions which have arisen during the conference. Then, there is a general discussion in which the microphone is passed to the speakers who wish to comment. S1 is the chair and organizes this and generally leads through the discussion.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone

Auis, however, not required to be bounded by a pause or a change of speaker, nor does it represent a turn in a conversation analytic sense. At a minimum, auis some phonetic production or noise made by a given speaker or a group of speakers.
